query: SELECT ef.id, ef.dataExecucao, CASE WHEN ef.dataExecucao IS NULL THEN 'NULL' ELSE 'HAS_VALUE' END as status FROM execucao_formando ef WHERE ef.formandoId = (SELECT id FROM formandos WHERE nome LIKE '%Aires%' LIMIT 1);
